      <title>随着 Wegovy 财富飙升，诺和诺德将关注范围扩大到心血管疾病</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-present-early-stage-trial-data-new-diabetes-drug-investor-meeting-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[诺和诺德公司(Novo Nordisk)因肥胖药物Wegovy的销售而财富飙升，该公司周四表示，正在扩大对糖尿病和减肥疗法的关注，将心血管疾病治疗纳入其中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-present-early-stage-trial-data-new-diabetes-drug-investor-meeting-2024-03-07/</guid>
