      <title>需求放缓，Hugo Boss 2024 年展望未达预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hugo-boss-expects-2024-operating-profit-below-market-expectations-2024-03-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Hugo Boss 周四预测 2024 年的销售额和营业利润低于市场预期，并表示 2025 年的销售目标可能会略有推迟，原因是消费者需求疲软，尤其是一些欧洲市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hugo-boss-expects-2024-operating-profit-below-market-expectations-2024-03-07/</guid>
